   Exercise 03a: Re-structuring the "Words of Wisdom" app.	  v01-00 31May12

   Contains:       Startup statements
                   Classes: WowView, WowModel, WowData.

   Pre-requisites: None.

   Description:    A re-structuring of the "Words of Wisdom" code.

   Changes:
